程式設計(二)(Program Design)





程式設計(二)
Program Design



評分：程式作業 25% 小考 25% 期中考 25% 期末考 25% 其它 10 %
參考用書：



C How to Program, 5th
                Edition, by Harvey M. Deitel , Paul J. Deitel.

The C programming
                Language, 2nd Editon, by Brian W. Kernighan and Dennis M. Ritchie,
                Prentice-Hall in 1988.


